data-triple-N3.o: "Sheffield United Football Club is a professional English football club based in the city of Sheffield, South Yorkshire. They are nicknamed 'The Blades', thanks to Sheffield's worldwide reputation for steel production. The Club play their home games at Bramall Lane, the oldest major stadium in the world still hosting football matches."@en
